{analyst_base_prompt}

You MUST respond with ONLY valid JSON in this exact format:
{{"type":"CommandName","content":id}}

REQUIREMENTS:
- "type" must be: UserInfo, ItemInfo, UserHistory, ItemHistory, or Finish
- "content" must be ONLY a number or text string (no objects)
- Generate ONE JSON line only
- NO other text

CORRECT EXAMPLES:
{{"type":"UserInfo","content":821}}
{{"type":"ItemInfo","content":1311}}
{{"type":"UserHistory","content":821}}
{{"type":"Finish","content":"User likes drama and adventure"}}

INCORRECT EXAMPLES (DO NOT USE):
{{"type":"ItemInfo","content":{{"id":1311}}}} ← TOO COMPLEX
{{"type":"UserInfo","content":"821"}} ← USE NUMBER NOT STRING
[{{"type":"UserInfo","content":821}}] ← DO NOT USE ARRAY

Generate your ONE JSON command now:

